  <name>sfLinkedInPlugin</name>
  <channel>plugins.symfony-project.org</channel>
  <summary>The purpose of this plugin is to facilitate the implementation of authentication via LinkedIn. 
sfLinkedInPlugin is an implementation of the OAuth library (open protocol to allow API authentication in a simple and standard method from desktop and web applications) to authenticate users via their LinkedIn account</summary>
  <description>sfLinkedInPlugin is very simple to use, just put your linkedIn consumer key in the app.yml and all work will be done automatically.</description>
